{
  "texts": [
    "For scoring the essays, following basic preprocessing, our system first segments the text into sections addressing the different learning tips.",
    "The resulting sections are coded individually following a scoring rubric.",
    "We collected and created datasets to train systems for both tasks.",
    "We evaluated two transformer-based architectures, GBERT and T5, and compared their performance against multiple bag-of-word baseline models.",
    "In the final step, the predicted scores are matched against a ground truth table offered by the course instructors, and the discrepancies are used to trigger rules populating a feedback template."
  ]
}